u need. You can use this feature for any table you might need to create; within Copilot, you\u0026#39;ll find an option to summarize the data in your spreadsheet.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWhile this feature will simplify summarization, you should still double-check to ensure everything is accurate.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"summarizing-lengthy-texts\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Summarizing Lengthy Texts\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to summarizing data, Microsoft Copilot is very good at giving you an overview of lengthy texts. You can either feed the software a PDF document and ask it to go through the information included in it or extract data from across the internet instead.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eYou\u0026#39;ll see everything in an easy-to-digest format once you\u0026#39;ve told Copilot to summarize your texts. This feature is handy whether you need an idea of longer books or to summarize study and meeting notes.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot-2025-03-19-at-14-34-51.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                      